    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240720/extras/beef244a29a00755ad9d8fdd2bc33951.poster.avif?t=1742261088\" width=416 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240720/extras/beef244a29a00755ad9d8fdd2bc33951.webm?t=1742261088\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240720/extras/beef244a29a00755ad9d8fdd2bc33951.mp4?t=1742261088\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >NONOTOWN 将经典的非绘图方块解谜体验提升到一个全新的水平，拥有四种独特的游戏模式。无论你是传统解谜爱好者，还是寻找更具动感的玩法，NONOTOWN 都有适合每个人的内容。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 <strong>经典</strong> 和 <strong>颜色</strong> 模式中，你需要使用逻辑和精确度，基于给出的数字线索填充网格。而真正的挑战在于我们创新的 <strong>块</strong> 和 <strong>色块</strong> 模式，玩家需要旋转预先填充的部分，使它们正确对齐，增加了新的难度层次。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240720/extras/0ab4ed8f88b90693c89cc136dba5588f.poster.avif?t=1742261088\" width=322 height=568 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240720/extras/0ab4ed8f88b90693c89cc136dba5588f.webm?t=1742261088\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240720/extras/0ab4ed8f88b90693c89cc136dba5588f.mp4?t=1742261088\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拥有 <strong>300 多个关卡</strong>，跨越所有模式，NONOTOWN 提供了无尽的解谜乐趣。每个模式都有其独特的策略，使得游戏对新手和资深非绘图方块爱好者都充满挑战与奖励。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁成就，挑战你的大脑，享受视觉丰富的解谜体验，让你一次又一次地回到游戏中。准备好掌握非绘图方块的艺术，并挑战这些块了吗？NONOTOWN 正在等待你！</p>",
